name: Joseph Lubin
tweet: As the development and unfolding of new and better systems accelerates, we look forward to Ethereum technology to enable a very broad swath of the population to have far greater economic and political agency than was possible under the infrastructure and systems pre 2020.

name: Joseph Lubin
tweet: We continue to demonstrate that this technology will serve as a new trust foundation for next-generation, increasingly decentralized, financial, economic, social, and political systems.

name: Joseph Lubin
tweet: and that this technology will prove a worthy evolutionary successor to that of Web 2 systems.

name: Joseph Lubin
tweet: While navigating hardship and the shock to our systems, our lives and those of family and friends, ConsenSys, the Ethereum ecosystem, and the broader decentralized protocol ecosystem demonstrated poignantly that we, like our Web 3 technology, are antifragile --

name: Joseph Lubin
tweet: The pandemic has shaped remote work in general, internet-based collaboration patterns, and the need to re-think global monetary and financial systems, global supply chains, trade and commerce, not to mention local and global governance systems.

name: Joseph Lubin
tweet: Little did we expect that mother nature would appear impatient with this already breakneck pace of progress, and light fires under our industry.

name: Joseph Lubin
tweet: And we expected some new trends to emerge and gain prominence. Yield farming, flash loans, CBDCs, the Baseline Protocol, cross-protocol bridges to Ethereum, and others emerged to push the envelope of exploration and development in novel dimensions.

name: Joseph Lubin
tweet: As we ushered in 2020 last year, we expected more of the same: L2 scalability (rollups and state channels), the launch of the first phase of #Ethereum 2.0, improved usability and security, more value in #DeFI, and more adoption of Enterprise Ethereum.

name: Joseph Lubin
tweet: Since inception in January 2014, every new year in the Ethereum ecosystem has promised enormous growth, breakthroughs, and an astonishing pace of development ‚Äî not to mention enormous creation of value: technical and other.
